OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FAs countries around the world gather
OL,8,Ffor COP29 in Azerbaijan, Zambia is
OL,9,Fsuffering its worst drought in 40
OL,10,Fyears and 50% of this year's crops
OL,11,Fhave been lost, ITV News Health and
OL,12,FScience Correspondent Martin Stew
OL,13,Freports
OL,15,FWords by ITV News Health and Science
OL,16,FProducer Rhiannon Hopley
OL,18,FWith 2024 on track to be the hottest
OL,19,Fyear ever, this week countries around
OL,20,Fthe world will gather for COP29 in
OL,21,FAzerbaijan.
