OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FOne of the main topics of discussion
OL,8,Fwill be climate finance - how much-
OL,9,Fdeveloped nations owe developing
OL,10,Fcountries to help them adapt to the
OL,11,Feffects of global warming.
OL,13,FUnder the 2015 Paris Agreement, rich
OL,14,Fcountries are bound to provide finance
OL,15,Fto developing countries to help them
OL,16,Fcut emissions and cope with the
OL,17,Feffects of climate change.
