OL,7,FThe current goal is to provide $100
OL,8,Fbillion (#77 billion) a year although
OL,9,Fit is widely agreed that this is not
OL,10,Fenough.
OL,12,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,13,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,14,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,15,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,17,FOne of the countries in need of this
OL,18,Fsupport is Zambia. It is suffering its
OL,19,Fworst drought in 40 years and 50% of
OL,20,Fthis year's crops have been lost.
