OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,F"We are at the frontlines of receiving
OL,8,Fthe adverse impacts of climate
OL,9,Fchange," says Gabriel Pollen, the
OL,10,Fnational coordinator for the country's
OL,11,Fdisaster management and mitigation
OL,12,Funit.
OL,14,F"We need to transition from merely
OL,15,Ftalking to dealing with the actual
OL,16,Frealities on the ground ` supporting
OL,17,Fdeveloping countries to build
OL,18,Fresilience in the face of climate
OL,19,Fchange."
