OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FZambia produces as many emissions in a
OL,8,Fyear as the UK does in ten days, and
OL,9,Fthe US produces in just 15 hours.
OL,11,FIt is also a leader in green energy `
OL,12,Fit provides 83% of its power through
OL,13,Fhydropower. Its biggest dam at Lake
OL,14,FKariba was completed in 1960.
OL,16,FBut the drought means the reservoir
OL,17,Fand the river systems which feed it
OL,18,Fare drying up.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/16
