OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FThe lake is currently running at just
OL,8,Fover 4% of its full capacity. Water
OL,9,Flevels have dropped to their lowest
OL,10,Fever from 13 metres to just 90cm.
OL,12,FCephas Museba, the senior power
OL,13,Fstation manager at the dam, says if
OL,14,Fthey continued to run power at
OL,15,Fcapacity they would run out of water
OL,16,Fin 30 days.
OL,18,FInstead, they are having to ration
OL,19,Fwhat they put through.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/16
