OL,3,CZambia running dry: What do rich
OL,4,Cnations owe countries on the climate
OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FJust one generator out of six is
OL,8,Frunning. The result is rolling power
OL,9,Foutages for Zambians. When we visited
OL,10,Fin early October, people were
OL,11,Freceiving just three hours of power a
OL,12,Fday ` usually in the middle of the
OL,13,Fnight.
OL,15,F"Climate change is real because the
OL,16,Feffect for us - we are already
OL,17,Fexperiencing it... The frequency of
OL,18,Fload shedding or drought will increase
OL,19,Fand for that we need to look for
OL,20,Fanother alternative source of power,"
OL,21,Fsays Museba.
