OL,7,FEven the traffic lights are not always
OL,8,Fswitched on, leaving drivers to
OL,9,Fnavigate the roads without them.
OL,11,FThe cost is especially high for small
OL,12,Fbusinesses.
OL,14,FAt Yellow Shop Barbershop, the owner
OL,15,FJulian Miti has had to cut his hours
OL,16,Fas he can only work during the
OL,17,Fdaylight.
