OL,5,Cfrontline?
OL,7,FShe says the cost of ice has increased
OL,8,Fdramatically in the last few months `
OL,9,Falmost quadrupling as demand for it
OL,10,Frises.
OL,12,FThe effects can also be seen starkly
OL,13,Foutside the big cities. Commercial
OL,14,Ffarmers who rely on power for their
OL,15,Fpump irrigation are having to plant
OL,16,Ffewer crops further increasing the
OL,17,Ffood crisis.
OL,19,FAt local health posts, vaccines are
OL,20,Falso being stored on ice and delivered
OL,21,Ffrom bigger cities to keep them cold.
