OL,7,FAt Chipapa Primary School in Chilanga,
OL,8,Fthey noticed female students were
OL,9,Foften staying home from school when
OL,10,Fthey were on their periods.
OL,12,FThe charity World Vision helped build
OL,13,Fa toilet block where the girls could
OL,14,Fwash and the school saw attendance
OL,15,Fincrease. But the block is now closed
OL,16,Fas without power, water cannot be
OL,17,Fpumped in.
