OL,7,F"It would be good if we could make use
OL,8,Fof solar systems that could power our
OL,9,Fhouses, communities and work systems.
OL,10,FOf course, we'd still need some money
OL,11,Fto pay for that."
OL,13,FWhile the charity sector is doing its
OL,14,Fbest to help the country's neediest to
OL,15,Ftackle the impacts of the drought, the
OL,16,Fgovernment is calling for support from
OL,17,Fother nations to build its climate
OL,18,Fresilience.
