OL,7,FIt argues that it needs funding to
OL,8,Fhelp promote investment in the overall
OL,9,Finfrastructure needed to cope with new
OL,10,Fextremes of weather, such as
OL,11,Fdiversifying the sources of
OL,12,Felectricity supply.
OL,14,F"We are receiving support to address
OL,15,Fthe impact of climate change but it's
OL,16,Ftailored towards immediate food
OL,17,Fassistance. Nothing is being given for
OL,18,Fresilience building in order for
OL,19,Fcountries like Zambia to better
OL,20,Fwithstand the adverse impacts of
OL,21,Fclimate change" says Gabriel Pollen.
